name: Skull Rambo
description: A young CroSkull reborn in BonesVille has an undead with a harsh childhood. Bullied since primary school, he had no friend who could help him. His days passed in melancholy and loneliness until, one day, while escaping from his bullies he locked himself inside Dr Jiko's laboratory. From there he came out evolved, armed to the teeth and with a thirst for revenge.
